      "writtenOn": "2015-09-28T07:59:50Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "There is a small layering violation here: android/base/ should only depend on system interfaces and itself (on the other hand android/utils/ can depend on android/base, system interfaces and itself).\n\nAnother point is that android/base/ is supposed to be a generic platform wrapper / helper base, while the SerialLine concept presented here is pretty much specific to Android emulation (really QEMU), so it might be better to put these definitions under android/emulation/ instead.",
      "revId": "6e91c884e0d90e27bbd7ae44c0878e0201f5b6d5",
